Game Notes
~~~~~~~~~~
Tib and Rob are the heroes of a wacky adventure that will teach them where
all of the bugs in our favorite games come from.
Have you ever played a rhythm game before? Well, this is like that, but much
better! With each note, you are responsible for the success of our two
heroes' quest. Swing your sword and shoot with your spacecraft to the beat of
chiptune tracks from Dubmood, Zabutom, Hello World, Yponeko, Le Plancton.
